At the same time, the Minister of Foreign Affairs Tobias Bilstron said that Sweden had all the conditions to join NATO and called on Turkey and Hungary to immediately revoke opposition to this step.

At the beginning of the NATO member State Foreign Minister's meeting held by Bilstron at Oslo, "Sweden has fulfilled all the commitments we made at the Madrid Summit last year, including new counter -terrorism legislation."

