China responded on Wednesday, accusing the US reconnaissance aircraft of "intentionally invading our training area" to implement the reconnaissance, and repeatedly held a "provocative and dangerous exercise."

On the occasion of these incidents, the tension between China and the United States has risen due to the Taiwan Strait problems and the Chinese meteorological airships fly over the United States earlier this year.

#### Conference discussion on the table

Analysts pointed out that there are expected other issues that will also become the primary topic of the dialogue, including Russia's war in Ukraine, the situation in Taiwan, and North Korea's weapon plans. However, Russia and North Korea will not send delegations to attend the meeting Essence

